# agent.skill

## Project Purpose

This project is a campus low-carbon and health mini-program. It combines task check-in, step and sport records, carbon saving points, campus activities, mall redemption, AI suggestions, and an AI Agent workbench. The Agent can plan daily actions based on user tasks, health data, completion history, weather, class schedule, and nearby sport venues.

## Directory Map

- `src/main/java/com/campus/carbon/`: Spring Boot backend source code.
- `src/main/resources/`: backend configuration and static admin page.
- `sql/`: database table creation and seed/update scripts.
- `uni-app项目/`: uni-app frontend source for WeChat mini-program.
- `比赛资料/`: competition documents and reference PDFs.
- `target/`: Maven build output, generated files, not source of truth.
- `uni-app项目/unpackage/`: uni-app compiled output, generated files, not source of truth.
- `.idea/`, `.vscode/`, `.claude/`, `carbon.iml`: local IDE/tool configuration.

## Root Files

- `pom.xml`: Spring Boot Maven project config, dependencies, Java version, MyBatis, OkHttp, Lombok, and build plugin.
- `README.md`: project notes and overview.
- `carbon.iml`: IntelliJ IDEA module file, local IDE metadata.
- `.gitattributes`: Git attribute rules.

## Backend Entry And Config

- `src/main/java/com/campus/carbon/CarbonApplication.java`: Spring Boot application entry point.
- `src/main/java/com/campus/carbon/config/CorsConfig.java`: CORS configuration so frontend/dev clients can call backend APIs.
- `src/main/java/com/campus/carbon/exception/GlobalExceptionHandler.java`: centralized exception handling for API errors.
- `src/main/resources/application.yml`: backend runtime config, including database, MyBatis camel-case mapping, AI, map, and weather related settings.
- `src/main/resources/static/admin/task-center.html`: static admin task-center page.

## Backend Utility

- `src/main/java/com/campus/carbon/util/CarbonMetrics.java`: shared carbon/points calculation helper methods.

