## Service Implementations

- `src/main/java/com/campus/carbon/service/impl/AiServiceImpl.java`: core AI and Agent logic. Builds suggestions, plans daily actions, scores tasks, verifies completion, uses memory, weather, schedule, and map venue signals.
- `src/main/java/com/campus/carbon/service/impl/ActivityTopicServiceImpl.java`: campus activity topic business logic.
- `src/main/java/com/campus/carbon/service/impl/AdminActivityServiceImpl.java`: admin activity management business logic.
- `src/main/java/com/campus/carbon/service/impl/AdminTaskServiceImpl.java`: admin task template management business logic.
- `src/main/java/com/campus/carbon/service/impl/HealthDataServiceImpl.java`: health data persistence and query logic.
- `src/main/java/com/campus/carbon/service/impl/MapVenueServiceImpl.java`: AMap nearby POI search and route planning logic for sport venues.
- `src/main/java/com/campus/carbon/service/impl/PointsServiceImpl.java`: points records, balance, and point changes.
- `src/main/java/com/campus/carbon/service/impl/ProductServiceImpl.java`: mall products and redemption logic.
- `src/main/java/com/campus/carbon/service/impl/RankServiceImpl.java`: ranking and leaderboard calculation.
- `src/main/java/com/campus/carbon/service/impl/SportRecordServiceImpl.java`: sport record management.
- `src/main/java/com/campus/carbon/service/impl/StepCountServiceImpl.java`: step count management.
- `src/main/java/com/campus/carbon/service/impl/StudentScheduleServiceImpl.java`: validates schedule input and converts today's class schedule into Agent planning context.
- `src/main/java/com/campus/carbon/service/impl/StudentServiceImpl.java`: student login/user lookup logic.
- `src/main/java/com/campus/carbon/service/impl/TaskServiceImpl.java`: task board assembly, task completion, rewards, and task status logic.
- `src/main/java/com/campus/carbon/service/impl/WeatherServiceImpl.java`: weather lookup and suitability judgment for indoor/outdoor Agent planning.

